25:10.944 --> 25:14.948
NO, NO, NO.
THAT'S NOT FAIR, SHEILA.
ADRIEN'S NEVER PLAYED.

25:14.991 --> 25:17.777
OH, NO, THAT'S OKAY.
I THINK I'M JUST GONNA WATCH.

25:17.820 --> 25:20.867
[ Greg ]
NO, NO.
YOU GOTTA PLAY, DOLL-FACE.

25:20.910 --> 25:23.652
NO SPECTATORS IN THIS GAME.[ Andy ]
