BESIDES, NO ONE HERE...</i>

25:35.272 --> 25:37.318
KNOWS YOUR DEEP,
DARK SECRETS.

25:37.361 --> 25:40.234
[ Andy ]
OH, NOT YET ANYWAY.

25:40.277 --> 25:43.933
SO, OKAY, YOU SAY-- YOU SAY--
