25:43.977 --> 25:45.500
OR JUST LIKE ME.

25:45.544 --> 25:47.589
I NEVER, UH--

25:49.069 --> 25:52.638
UH-- I NEVER SLEPT
WITH MY MOM'S BOYFRIEND.

25:52.681 --> 25:54.814
<i>- WHOA!
