- UGH! HELENA!

26:15.748 --> 26:18.707
I THOUGHT YOU SAID YOU WERE
GIVING HER TENNIS LESSONS.

26:18.751 --> 26:19.882
NASTY!

26:21.405 --> 26:23.930
[ Kelly ]
OKAY, UM--

26:23.973 --> 26:25.018
OKAY, IT'S MY TURN.

26:25.061 --> 26:28.587
UM, I NEVER, UM--

26:30.632 --> 26:33.679
