WITH THE HELP.

26:41.556 --> 26:42.731
WOW.

26:42.775 --> 26:45.865
-IT'S BEEN FUN.
-YEAH.

26:45.908 --> 26:47.736
GOODNIGHT.

26:51.479 --> 26:53.829
IT'S JUST
A GAME.

26:53.873 --> 26:56.266
WAIT! ADRIEN!

26:56.310 --> 26:59.618
