ONE OF MY RULES.

27:04.448 --> 27:07.800
NO ONE LEAVES
MY PARTIES UNHAPPY.

27:07.843 --> 27:11.412
- THAT WAS SOME
NEAT WORK THERE, KEL.
- THANK YOU.

27:11.455 --> 27:14.197
<i>YEAH, WELL, I FORGOT.
YOU LEARNED FROM
THE MASTER, DIDN'T YOU?</i>

27:14.241 --> 27:16.809
<i>[ Andy ]
I THOUGHT IT WAS FUNNY.</i>

27:16.852 --> 27:19.725
THEY TOTALLY
WALKED AWAY.

27:19.768 --> 27:25.992
YOU KNOW, SOMETIMES I THINK
I HAVE THESE PARTIES JUST
SO I CAN SNEAK AWAY AND HIDE.

27:26.035 --> 27:29.604
I CAN THINK
OF CHEAPER WAYS TO BE ALONE.

27:29.648 --> 27:34.087
WELL, IT PROBABLY GOES BACK
TO WHEN WE WERE KIDS.

27:34.130 --> 27:39.658
MY SISTER AND I USED TO COME
DOWN HERE TO GET AWAY FROM
THOSE BORING CLUB PARTIES.

27:41.311 --> 27:44.924
IT'S WEIRD, BUT
IT'S KIND OF LIKE THAT NOW.

27:46.447 --> 27:48.231
BEING HERE WITH YOU.

27:51.191 --> 27:54.498
DOES SHE STILL COME
-TO THE CLUB OFTEN?
-OH, NO, NO, NO, NO.

27:54.542 --> 27:58.677
SHE HATED THE CLUB.
SHE HATED EVERYTHING
ABOUT THIS TOWN.

27:58.720 --> 28:02.593
COULDN'T WAIT TO GET OUT.
NOT THAT I BLAME HER.
IT'S JUST--

28:02.637 --> 28:04.857
IT'S KIND OF HARD.

28:07.468 --> 28:09.122
SHE JUST TOOK OFF?

28:10.689 --> 28:13.692
PRETTY COOL, HUH?

28:13.735 --> 28:17.043
WE STILL GET POSTCARDS FROM
HER, MY DAD AND I, BUT, UM,

28:18.522 --> 28:20.307
IT'S NOT THE SAME.

28:22.091 --> 28:23.789
YOU MISS HER.

28:26.008 --> 28:29.011
OH!
SORRY ABOUT THAT.

28:29.055 --> 28:32.449
DIDN'T MEAN
TO GET YOU ALL WET.

28:43.809 --> 28:46.072
