YOU'RE NOT WORKING TODAY.

28:46.115 --> 28:50.554
-YEAH, I GOT THE DAY OFF.
-YOU ALRIGHT?
YOU LOOK A LITTLE TIRED.

28:50.598 --> 28:55.646
LISTEN, UM, SORRY, DOC.
I GOTTA GO. I'M LATE.

28:58.388 --> 29:00.651
HI, DOCTOR.

29:00.695 --> 29:02.741
FIRST WE'RE GOING
TO SEE LUIS.

29:02.784 --> 29:07.267
<i>NOW, THIS IS A LUXURY I COULD DEFINITELY GET USED TO.</i>

29:07.310 --> 29:13.142
<i>OOH, THOSE POOR BOYS
AT THAT CLUB! LOOK
AT THE TWO OF YOU. MMM!</i>

29:13.186 --> 29:17.625
THE BODIES THAT LAUNCHED
ONE THOUSAND COLD SHOWERS.

29:17.668 --> 29:20.062
OH, MORE THAN
A THOUSAND, HONEY.

29:20.106 --> 29:22.804
<i>ONE THING I KNOW BETTER
THAN HAIR IS BOYS.</i>

29:22.848 --> 29:28.070
<i>LET ME TELL YOU
SOMETHING,
THE TWO OF YOU ARE BOTH PIECES
OF HARD CANDY.</i>

29:28.114 --> 29:31.117
NOW, LUIS, YOU'RE NOT
JEALOUS MUCH, ARE YOU?

29:31.160 --> 29:34.555
OH, DON'T YOU DARE
OUT-BITCH ME, GIRL.

29:34.598 --> 29:38.124
<i>YOU THANK YOUR LUCKY STARS
THAT I WAS NOT BORN
IN THE SISTERHOOD, HONEY,</i>

29:38.167 --> 29:42.389
BECAUSE I WOULD ROCK
YOUR WORLD UPSIDE DOWN,

29:42.432 --> 29:44.913
MISS BRITTANY FOSTER.

29:44.957 --> 29:49.178
HE'S CRAZY, BUT YOU KNOW WHAT?
HE'S RIGHT. THE GUYS ARE GONNA
BE ALL OVER YOU.

29:49.222 --> 29:52.965
I AM REALLY NOT
IN THE MARKET.

29:53.008 --> 29:54.880
OKAY, OKAY.

29:54.923 --> 29:57.447
OH, WOW.

29:57.491 --> 30:02.801
OH, ADRIEN,
YOU WOULD KILL IN THAT DRESS.

30:02.844 --> 30:04.237
ALL DONE, LADIES.

30:05.716 --> 30:07.849
LOOK.

30:09.285 --> 30:11.592
NOW WE REALLY ARE
LIKE SISTERS.

30:13.942 --> 30:17.772
♪ SOMETIMES
I JUST CAN'T TELL ♪

30:17.816 --> 30:20.601
♪ CAN I LET MYSELF GO

30:21.950 --> 30:25.475
