30:29.871 --> 30:33.483
♪ I FEEL LIKE
I FOUND A PLACE ♪

30:33.527 --> 30:37.748
♪ WARM AS MY DESIRE

30:37.792 --> 30:41.317
♪ I THINK
THAT TO HESITATE ♪

30:41.361 --> 30:47.019
♪ WOULD BE LIKE POURIN' SAND
UPON THAT FIRE ♪

30:47.062 --> 30:50.936
♪ LOOK AT THIS
CRAZY FACE ♪

30:50.979 --> 30:55.810
♪ DON'T LOOK AROUND
FROM YOUR INSIDES, BABY ♪

30:55.854 --> 30:57.507
YOU KNOW, ADRIEN,

30:57.551 --> 31:00.249
YOU MIGHT TRY SPREADING
